<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">叮咚~</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">让小编带你回顾一下~</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">开启江软经管限定版</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">“我有你没有”吧！</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">准备好了吗？</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">游戏要开始啦！</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">【游戏规则】</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">游戏开始前</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">大家伸出一只手掌</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">接下来，小编会举例五件事</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">如果哪一件你做过</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">就弯曲一根手指</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">弯曲手指最多的人就获胜啦！</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">1.争做劳动先锋</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">你可曾种过地、大扫除、志愿服务</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">体会到一起集体劳动的快乐</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">在平凡的生活中</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">耕耘自己，安顿自己</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718170117276023736.png" title="1718170117276023736.png" style="text-align: center; white-space: normal;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718170115805057852.png" style="" title="1718170115805057852.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718170116664072139.png" style="" title="1718170116664072139.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718170117212089501.png" style="" title="1718170117212089501.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718170117259092371.png" style="" title="1718170117259092371.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">劳动是一切幸福的源泉</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">动动手，流流汗</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">强健了体魄</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">增强了才能</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718170264004057839.png" title="1718170264004057839.png" style="text-align: center; white-space: normal;"/></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718170263913086053.png" title="1718170263913086053.png" style="text-align: center; white-space: normal;"/></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718170263837050946.png" style="" title="1718170263837050946.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">2.争做运动先锋</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">你可曾体验过在运动的时候</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">体验到汗水肆意挥洒的快感</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">享受烦恼抛诸脑后的当下</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">洒下的汗水</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">在阳光下熠熠生辉</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br/></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718170366880034194.png" style="" title="1718170366880034194.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718170367079039728.png" style="" title="1718170367079039728.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">运动，多么骄傲</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">它让生命之树常青</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">双手摆动着青春</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">双腿凝聚着力量</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">运动场地浸透着青春活力</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718170410916097118.png" style="" title="1718170410916097118.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718170411925025324.png" style="" title="1718170411925025324.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">3.争做快乐先锋</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">你可曾参加过学校举办的各种活动</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">丰富多彩，有趣有益</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">在各种各样的学校活动里</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">我们可以</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">尽情地释放自己的能量</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"></span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718170492562051282.png" style="width: 984px; height: 682px;" title="1718170492562051282.png" width="984" height="682"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718170493207070712.png" style="" title="1718170493207070712.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240612/1718170493583029322.png" style="" title="1718170493583029322.png"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">积极参与，充实自我</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">勇敢展现，广交良友</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-fami